title: Dell PowerVault ME5: Connected Hosts
agents: dell_powervault_me5
catalog: hw/storagehw/dell
license: GPLv2
distribution: Sher Zaman
description:
 Monitors the initiators connected to a Dell PowerVault ME5 system. An initiator
 is discovered while it is connected, establishing a baseline; if it later
 reports disconnected or is no longer present in the initiator table, the
 service raises.

 Conditions are configurable via the "Dell PowerVault ME5 connected host"
 ruleset.

item:
 The initiator nickname or id.

discovery:
 One service is created per connected initiator.
